Demographic Questions

We are collecting demographic data on our participants this year. Your answers will be shared only in the aggregate and will be kept confidential on the individual level.

Answering the demographic questions is not required for registration.

Meeting Pricing

SSA members attend the Annual Meeting at a discounted rate. See the registration fee chart on our website for more information.

Residents of a country with a low or low-middle income economy as determined by The World Bank receive discounted registration. Let us know if you qualify for this reduced registration under the “Registration Fee” section below.

If you have any questions about your registration, please email us at info@seismosoc.org.

Meeting Pricing

Our records indicate you are not an SSA member. If you believe this is incorrect, please email us at info@seismosoc.org. SSA members attend the Annual Meeting at a discounted rate. See the registration fee chart on our website for more information.

If you register as a non-member, you will receive full benefits of SSA membership for one year. Learn more here.

Members of the Latin American and Caribbean Seismological Commission (LACSC) or the Seismological Society of China (SSC) may register for the SSA Annual Meeting at the SSA member rate and will not receive an SSA membership with registration. Let us know if you are an SSC or LACSC member by using the button below.

Residents of a country with a low or low-middle income economy as determined by The World Bank receive discounted registration. Let us know if you qualify for this reduced registration under the “Registration Fee” section below.

Affiliate members do not receive a discounted registration to the Annual Meeting. If you would like to become an SSA Regular Member, contact info@seismosoc.org.

If you have any questions, please email info@seismosoc.org.

Registration Fee *

The below registration price reflects the discount for your member type.
